OUR HISTORY
History
Past MVPs
The most valuable player award is named after Tom Starr who help start our Fort Worth bowl game and was the first Executive Director of the Armed Forces Bowl. Starr served in Vietnam and was the recipient of a Bronze Star, two Joint Service Commendation Medals, a Vietnam Service Medal and a Vietnam Campaign Medal.
